Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:18.18,OPe,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}The winds whisper of my next chapter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.18,0:01:23.06,OPe,,0,0,0,,{The night's glow drawn anew}Nights glistening anew with sorcery
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:26.02,OPe,,0,0,0,,I can barely stand to let the ink dry{The ink cannot dry fast enough}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:29.90,OPe,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}I've been waiting for this all along
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:34.32,OPe,,0,0,0,,So much to learn that I hardly know where to begin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:39.08,OPe,,0,0,0,,But even though I don't think I'm all that special
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.08,0:01:46.67,OPe,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,450)}I won't stray from the path that leads to my dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:52.22,OPe,,0,0,0,,My voice and yours in unison
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:55.60,OPe,,0,0,0,,As if fate meant to bring us together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:59.39,OPe,,0,0,0,,An anthem built from our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:02:03.73,OPe,,0,0,0,,Every note a prayer held dear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.73,0:02:07.65,OPe,,0,0,0,,All I've hoped and longed for so much{more than anyone}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.65,0:02:11.90,OPe,,0,0,0,,{This magic is what truly gives color to life}{The beauty of life is its own magic}Giving life color is its own magic
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:16.78,OPe,,0,0,0,,Even if I am ever without this power
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:20.58,OPe,,0,0,0,,Each step will take me that much closer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.58,0:02:22.91,OPe,,0,0,0,,Every day a new wonder
